<h1 class="gl-mb-5 gl-text-size-h2 gl-hidden md:gl-block">
Gitlab @ CCI
</h1>
<div id="js-custom-sign-in-description"><p data-sourcepos="1:1-1:52" dir="auto">Gitlab is for Drexel CCI students and collaborators.</p>&#x000A;<p data-sourcepos="3:1-3:108" dir="auto">CCI Students, Faculty and Staff should log in using the "DrexelConnect" login method below the sign-in area.</p>&#x000A;<p data-sourcepos="5:1-5:147" dir="auto">If you're an external collaborator, please have a CCI faculty or staff member email <a data-sourcepos="5:85-5:100" href="mailto:ihelp@drexel.edu">ihelp@drexel.edu</a> to request that an account be created for you.</p></div>
</div>
</div>
